function waitFor({ key, sub }, callback) {
if (window[key]) {
if (sub) {
if (window[key][sub]) {
callback();
} else {
setTimeout(() => waitFor({ key, sub }, callback), 100);
}
} else {
callback();
}
} else {
setTimeout(() => waitFor({ key, sub }, callback), 100);
}
}

(scopeRoot.closest && scopeRoot.closest('[data-tbsp-component-type="grid"]'))
)) ||
(!scopeRoot && document.querySelector('.grid, [data-tbsp-component-type="grid"]'))
);

var inUpsellCarousel = !!(
(scopeRoot && (
(scopeRoot.getAttribute && scopeRoot.getAttribute('data-tbsp-component-type') === 'upsell') ||
(scopeRoot.closest && scopeRoot.closest('[data-tbsp-component-type="upsell"]')) ||
(scopeRoot.closest && scopeRoot.closest('[data-mtr-section="upsell carousel"]'))
)) ||
(!scopeRoot && (document.querySelector('[data-tbsp-component-type="upsell"]') || document.querySelector('[data-mtr-section="upsell carousel"]')))
);

var inProductCarousel = !!(
(scopeRoot && (
(scopeRoot.getAttribute && scopeRoot.getAttribute('data-tbsp-component-type') === 'product') ||
(scopeRoot.closest && scopeRoot.closest('[data-tbsp-component-type="product"]')) ||
(scopeRoot.closest && scopeRoot.closest('[data-mtr-section="product carousel"]'))
)) ||
(!scopeRoot && (document.querySelector('[data-tbsp-component-type="product"]') || document.querySelector('[data-mtr-section="product carousel"]')))
);

// Determine template ID using switch statement for readability
var templateId;
switch (true) {
case inNavSearch:
templateId = 'shoplift-lcs-template-nav';
break;
case inGridLayout:
templateId = 'shoplift-lcs-template-grid';
break;
case inUpsellCarousel:
templateId = 'shoplift-lcs-template-upsell-carousel';
break;
case inProductCarousel:
templateId = 'shoplift-lcs-template-product-carousel';
break;
default:
templateId = 'shoplift-lcs-template-collection-carousel';
break;
}
var tpl = document.getElementById(templateId);
if (!tpl) {
return null;
}

var fragment = tpl.content ? tpl.content.cloneNode(true) : null;
if (!fragment) {
var tmp = document.createElement('div');
tmp.innerHTML = tpl.innerHTML || '';
fragment = tmp;
}

// Try known Tablescape product card roots (carousel/grid) then fall back to a generic root
var root =
fragment.querySelector('[data-tbsp-component="productCardCarousel"]') ||
fragment.querySelector('[data-tbsp-component^="productCard"]') ||
fragment.querySelector('[data-mtr-product-id]') ||
fragment.firstElementChild ||
null;



return root;
}

function swapCards(product) {
var CANONICAL_CARD = getCanonicalCardRoot(null);
var cards = document.querySelectorAll('[data-mtr-product-id="' + TARGET_PRODUCT_ID + '"]');
if (!cards.length) {
return;
}

cards.forEach(function (card, index) {

// Full replacement path: swap the entire product card to the canonical variant card
if (CANONICAL_CARD) {
var newCard = CANONICAL_CARD.cloneNode(true);
newCard.setAttribute('class', card.getAttribute('class'));
newCard.setAttribute('data-shoplift-replaced', 'true');
if (card.parentNode) {
card.parentNode.replaceChild(newCard, card);
}
return; // Leave Splide behavior to the framework
}
});
}

// Use replacement product data from theme settings (no fetch needed)
// Initial attempt
swapCards(REPLACEMENT);

// Use requestAnimationFrame for fastest possible detection
var startTime = Date.now();
var maxDuration = 10000; // 10 seconds

function checkForCards() {
var cards = document.querySelectorAll('[data-mtr-product-id="' + TARGET_PRODUCT_ID + '"]');
if (cards.length > 0) {
swapCards(REPLACEMENT);
return; // Stop checking once cards are found
}

// Continue checking if we haven't exceeded the max duration
if (Date.now() - startTime < maxDuration) {
requestAnimationFrame(checkForCards);
} else {
}
}

// Start the RAF loop
requestAnimationFrame(checkForCards);

// --- Predictive Search (Navigation Search) support ---
// Replace newly injected predictive search product cards by observing the container
function swapCardsInScope(scopeRoot) {
if (!scopeRoot) return 0;
var CANONICAL_CARD = getCanonicalCardRoot(scopeRoot);
if (!CANONICAL_CARD) return 0;
var scopedCards = scopeRoot.querySelectorAll('[data-mtr-product-id="' + TARGET_PRODUCT_ID + '"]:not([data-shoplift-replaced])');
if (!scopedCards.length) return 0;
var replacedCount = 0;
scopedCards.forEach(function (card) {
var newCard = CANONICAL_CARD.cloneNode(true);
newCard.setAttribute('data-shoplift-replaced', 'true');
if (card.parentNode) {
card.parentNode.replaceChild(newCard, card);
}
replacedCount++;
});
return replacedCount;
}

function setupPredictiveSearchObservers() {
var root = document.body;
if (!root || !window.MutationObserver) return;


// Immediate pass if results are already present
var existing = document.querySelector('.nav-search-results');
if (existing) {
var initialReplaced = swapCardsInScope(existing);
if (initialReplaced > 0) {
return;
}
}

// Observe global mutations and run scoped swap when results render
var rafScheduled = false;
var mo = new MutationObserver(function () {
if (rafScheduled) return;
rafScheduled = true;
requestAnimationFrame(function () {
rafScheduled = false;
var container = document.querySelector('.nav-search-results');
if (container) {
var replaced = swapCardsInScope(container);
if (replaced > 0) {
mo.disconnect();
}
}
});
});
mo.observe(root, { childList: true, subtree: true });
}

// When predictive search section markup is injected, perform scoped swap and attach observer
window.addEventListener('shopify:section:load', function () {
setupPredictiveSearchObservers();
});

// No eager setup; re-arm observer on each predictive search render via section:load
} catch (e) {}
})();
</script>

(() => {
function waitFor({ key, sub }, callback) {
if (window[key]) {
if (sub) {
if (window[key][sub]) {
callback();
} else {
setTimeout(() => waitFor({ key, sub }, callback), 100);
}
} else {
callback();
}
} else {
setTimeout(() => waitFor({ key, sub }, callback), 100);
}
}

{
key: '__attentive',
sub: 'trigger',
},
() => {
const creativeIds = {
90: { mobile: 1062695, desktop: 1062694 },

365: { mobile: 1064384, desktop: 1064388 },
};

if (!_opcx) {
return;
}

return;
